<p>But then we have</p>
<div class="math notranslate nohighlight">
<span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"><span class="MJXp-math MJXp-display" id="MJXp-Span-786"><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-787">n</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-788" style="margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;">=</span><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-789">m</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-790" style="margin-left: 0.267em; margin-right: 0.267em;">⋅</span><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-791">k</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-792" style="margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;">=</span><span class="MJXp-msubsup" id="MJXp-Span-793"><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-794" style="margin-right: 0.05em;">p</span><span class="MJXp-mn MJXp-script" id="MJXp-Span-795" style="vertical-align: -0.4em;">1</span></span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-796" style="margin-left: 0.267em; margin-right: 0.267em;">⋅</span><span class="MJXp-msubsup" id="MJXp-Span-797"><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-798" style="margin-right: 0.05em;">p</span><span class="MJXp-mn MJXp-script" id="MJXp-Span-799" style="vertical-align: -0.4em;">2</span></span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-800" style="margin-left: 0.267em; margin-right: 0.267em;">⋅</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-801" style="margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;">…</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-802" style="margin-left: 0.267em; margin-right: 0.267em;">⋅</span><span class="MJXp-msubsup" id="MJXp-Span-803"><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-804" style="margin-right: 0.05em;">p</span><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic MJXp-script" id="MJXp-Span-805" style="vertical-align: -0.4em;">u</span></span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-806" style="margin-left: 0.267em; margin-right: 0.267em;">⋅</span><span class="MJXp-msubsup" id="MJXp-Span-807"><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-808" style="margin-right: 0.05em;">q</span><span class="MJXp-mn MJXp-script" id="M