<p>What can you infer about <span class="math notranslate nohighlight"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"><span class="MJXp-math" id="MJXp-Span-1017"><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1018">f</span></span></span><span class="MathJax MathJax_Processed" id="MathJax-Element-206-Frame" tabindex="0" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1247"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0em; height: 0px; font-size: 124%;"><span style="position: absolute;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1248"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1249" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">f<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.06em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span></nobr></span></span>? Try calculating a few values:</p>
<div class="math notranslate nohighlight">
