><span class="mtd" id="MathJax-Span-1501"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1502"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1503"></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1504" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.278em;">=</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1505" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.278em;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1506" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1507" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.222em;">+</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1508" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.222em;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1509" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1510" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.222em;">⋅</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1511" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.222em;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.003em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1512" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1513" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1514" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.985em;"></span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.985em;"></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></nobr></span></div></div>
<p>Try calculating the first few values. Unwrapping the definition, we see that <span class="math notranslate nohighlight"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"><span class="MJXp-math" id="MJXp-Span-1250"><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1251">g</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1252" style="margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;">(</span><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1253">n</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1254" style="margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;">)</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1255" style="margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;">=</span><span class="MJXp-mn" id="MJXp-Span-1256">1</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1257" style="margin-left: 0.267em; margin-right: 0.267em;">⋅</span><span class="MJXp-mn" id="MJXp-Span-1258">2</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1259" style="margin-left: 0.267em; margin-right: 0.267em;">⋅</span><span class="MJXp-mn" id="MJXp-Span-1260">3</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1261" style="margin-left: 0.267em; margin-right: 0.267em;">⋅</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1262" style="margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;">…</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1263" style="margin-left: 0.267em; margin-right: 0.267em;">⋅</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1264" style="margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;">(</span><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1265">n</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1266" style="margin-left: 0.267em; margin-right: 0.267em;">−</span><span class="MJXp-mn" id="MJXp-Span-1267">1</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1268" style="margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;">)</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1269" style="margin-left: 0.267em; margin-right: 0.267em;">⋅</span><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1270">n</span></span></span><span class="MathJax MathJax_Processed" id="MathJax-Element-230-Frame" tabindex="0" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1515"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0em; height: 0px; font-size: 124%;"><span style="position: absolute;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1516"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1517" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.003em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1518" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1519" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1520" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1521" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.278em;">=</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1522" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.278em;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1523" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.222em;">⋅</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1524" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.222em;">2</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1525" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.222em;">⋅</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1526" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.222em;">3</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1527" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.222em;">⋅</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1528" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.222em;">…</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1529" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.222em;">⋅</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1530" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.222em;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1531" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1532" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.222em;">−</span><span class="mn" id="MathJax-Span-1533" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.222em;">1</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1534" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1535" style="font-family: MathJax_Main; padding-left: 0.222em;">⋅</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1536" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic; padding-left: 0.222em;">n</span></span></span></span></span></nobr></span></span> for every <span class="math notranslate nohighlight"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"><span class="MJXp-math" id="MJXp-Span-1271"><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1272">n</span></span></span><span class="MathJax MathJax_Processed" id="MathJax-Element-231-Frame" tabindex="0" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1537"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0em; height: 0px; font-size: 124%;"><span style="position: absolute;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1538"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1539" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span></span></span></span></span></nobr></span></span>; indeed, definition by recursion is usually the proper way to make expressions using “…” precise. The value <span class="math notranslate nohighlight"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"><span class="MJXp-math" id="MJXp-Span-1273"><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1274">g</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1275" style="margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;">(</span><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1276">n</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1277" style="margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;">)</span></span></span><span class="MathJax MathJax_Processed" id="MathJax-Element-232-Frame" tabindex="0" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1540"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0em; height: 0px; font-size: 124%;"><span style="position: absolute;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1541"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1542" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">g<span style="display: inline-block; overflow: hidden; height: 1px; width: 0.003em;"></span></span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1543" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">(</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1544" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1545" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">)</span></span></span></span></span></nobr></span></span> is read “<span class="math notranslate nohighlight"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"><span class="MJXp-math" id="MJXp-Span-1278"><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1279">n</span></span></span><span class="MathJax MathJax_Processed" id="MathJax-Element-233-Frame" tabindex="0" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1546"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0em; height: 0px; font-size: 124%;"><span style="position: absolute;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1547"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1548" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span></span></span></span></span></nobr></span></span> factorial,” and written <span class="math notranslate nohighlight"><span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"><span class="MJXp-math" id="MJXp-Span-1280"><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1281">n</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1282" style="margin-left: 0.111em; margin-right: 0em;">!</span></span></span><span class="MathJax MathJax_Processed" id="MathJax-Element-234-Frame" tabindex="0" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1549"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0em; height: 0px; font-size: 124%;"><span style="position: absolute;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1550"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1551" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1552" style="font-family: MathJax_Main;">!</span></span></span></span></span></nobr></span></span>.</p>
<p>Indeed, summation notation</p>
<div class="math notranslate nohighlight">
<span class="MathJax_Preview" style="color: inherit;"><span class="MJXp-math MJXp-display" id="MJXp-Span-1283"><span class="MJXp-munderover" id="MJXp-Span-1284"><span class=""><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1285" style="margin-left: 0.111em; margin-right: 0.167em;"><span class="MJXp-largeop">∑</span></span></span><span class=" MJXp-script"><span class="MJXp-mrow" id="MJXp-Span-1286" style="margin-left: 0px;"><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1287">i</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1288">&lt;</span><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1289">n</span></span></span></span><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1290">f</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1291" style="margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;">(</span><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1292">i</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1293" style="margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;">)</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1294" style="margin-left: 0.333em; margin-right: 0.333em;">=</span><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1295">f</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1296" style="margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;">(</span><span class="MJXp-mn" id="MJXp-Span-1297">0</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1298" style="margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;">)</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1299" style="margin-left: 0.267em; margin-right: 0.267em;">+</span><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1300">f</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1301" style="margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;">(</span><span class="MJXp-mn" id="MJXp-Span-1302">1</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1303" style="margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;">)</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1304" style="margin-left: 0.267em; margin-right: 0.267em;">+</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1305" style="margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;">…</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1306" style="margin-left: 0.267em; margin-right: 0.267em;">+</span><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1307">f</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1308" style="margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;">(</span><span class="MJXp-mi MJXp-italic" id="MJXp-Span-1309">n</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1310" style="margin-left: 0.267em; margin-right: 0.267em;">−</span><span class="MJXp-mn" id="MJXp-Span-1311">1</span><span class="MJXp-mo" id="MJXp-Span-1312" style="margin-left: 0em; margin-right: 0em;">)</span></span></span><div class="MathJax_Display MathJax_Processed"><span class="MathJax" id="MathJax-Element-235-Frame" tabindex="0" style=""><nobr><span class="math" id="MathJax-Span-1553"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 0em; height: 0px; font-size: 124%;"><span style="position: absolute;"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1554"><span class="munderover" id="MathJax-Span-1555"><span style="display: inline-block; position: relative; width: 1.444em; height: 0px;"><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(2.893em, 1001.39em, 4.577em, -1000em); top: -3.985em; left: 0em;"><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1556" style="font-family: MathJax_Size2; vertical-align: 0em;">∑</span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.985em;"></span></span><span style="position: absolute; clip: rect(3.375em, 1001.2em, 4.255em, -1000em); top: -2.901em; left: 0.113em;"><span class="texatom" id="MathJax-Span-1557"><span class="mrow" id="MathJax-Span-1558"><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1559" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">i</span><span class="mo" id="MathJax-Span-1560" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Main;">&lt;</span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1561" style="font-size: 70.7%; font-family: MathJax_Math-italic;">n</span></span></span><span style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; height: 3.985em;"></span></span></span></span><span class="mi" id="MathJax-Span-1562" style="font-family: MathJax_Math-ital